close_reason: "Implemented: HTML export has today-col CSS class with ▼ today marker, parity with ASCII/Mermaid."
body: "ASCII already prints a TODAY caret row and Mermaid emits a today comment, but the HTML export has no today indicator. Add a highlighted/colored vertical column (the week column containing opts.today) to the HTML table header and body cells, rendered only when today falls within the chart window. Keep alignment intact."
